======================================================================

n=4: max H = 5, achieved by 24 tournaments
  #odd cycles: 2
  #conflict edges: 1
  Independence number α(Ω): 1
  I(Ω, 2) = 5
  log₂(H) ≈ 2.3219

n=5: max H = 15, achieved by 64 tournaments
  #odd cycles: 5
  #conflict edges: 10
